metadata.name: Time Traveler Open Edition #1
metadata.description:
The Time Travelers personify the infinite creative consciousness that we all share. 
Hand-drawn original art by Sarkis Delimelkon also known as SARKISM using Procreate app on the iPad Pro. All art is created intuitively without visual reference.

*Time Limited* This open edition will be capped at the max number of tokens minted within 24 hours.

Dimensions:  
7000px X 9300px 
300dpi  
17.5MB

This piece was inspired by the synchronicities and connections that took place during the week of NFT NYC 2023. 
The Time Travelers personify the infinite creative consciousness that we all share.
